 offers an innovative understanding of a tumultuous time of decolonization.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 0aCommodificationzFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aFeminine beauty (Aesthetics)xEconomic aspectszFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aFemininityxEconomic aspectszFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aNational characteristics, FrenchxHistoryy20th century. 0aTourismzFrancexHistoryy20th century. 0aWomenzFrancexHistoryy20th century. 7aHISTORY / Europe / France.2bisacsh  aAir France.  aBrigitte Bardot.  aEurope.  aFrench history.  aFrench tourism.  aOlympic hostess.  aair hostess.  agender.  ahostess fashions.  apostwar France.  aromantic.  asoft power.  astewardess.  awomen’s history.40uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978148753808840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487538088423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781487538088/original  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK